This paper discusses trust mechanisms in grid computing, which is a topic related to security (cs.CR) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions reputation systems, which are commonly used in distributed systems (cs.DS) and networking (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper proposes a mechanism for identifying and purging untrustworthy entities, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
